channel.title: Need to demote all admins please help me!
channel.description:
Ok, I'm using Allstar-scape V2 and there are too many admins that my brother made!! I need to know how to view all the admins on the server. Once, I saw a program in a source that showed you all the players stats, password, and if they're admin and stuff. Can anyone help? I need to demote all staff and I can't!
So anyway, it's to hard to go one by one. I need a program like the one I mentioned above.
